2709327/spkgkndhtjzm8ctd4urf.png"}}, {"model": "properties.property", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "Luxury 3BHK Villa with Private Garden", "slug": "luxury-3bhk-villa-with-private-garden", "description": "A beautifully designed 3BHK luxury villa located in a premium gated community in Kochi. This modern home features spacious bedrooms, a large living area with natural lighting, modular kitchen, landscaped private garden, covered parking, and 24/7 security. Perfect for families looking for comfort, privacy, and a premium lifestyle. Close to schools, hospitals, shopping malls, and major road access.", "price": "12500000.00", "location": "Kakkanad, Kochi, Kerala", "category": 1, "owner": null, "agent": 1, "listing_type": "Sale", "bedrooms": 0, "bathrooms": 0, "area": 0, "latitude": null, "longitude": null, "featured_image": "image/upload/v1773044406/tudl6fnk8rgj1mtgpaj7.png", "is_featured": true, "is_available": true, "created_at": "2026-02-26T06:52:44.852Z"}}, {"model": "properties.property", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Modern Warehouse Facility with Loading Dock √ Kalamassery", "slug": "modern-warehouse-kalamassery-kochi", "description": "Spacious industrial warehouse located in the prime industrial hub of Kalamassery, Kochi. This property features a high-clearance ceiling, multiple loading docks, wide entry gate for container trucks, dedicated office cabin, staff restrooms, and 3-phase power connection. Ideal for logistics, storage, distribution, or light manufacturing operations. Easy access to NH66 and Cochin Port.", "price": "37500000.00", "location": "Kalamassery, Kochi, Kerala", "category": 2, "owner": null, "agent": 2, "listing_type": "Rent", "bedrooms": 0, "bathrooms": 0, "area": 0, "latitude": null, "longitude": null, "featured_image": "image/upload/v1773038513/xystkjgoajmswcerpvxa.png", "is_featured": true, "is_available": true, "created_at": "2026-02-27T11:19:27.385Z"}}, {"model": "properties.property", "pk": 4, "fields": {"title": "Premium 4BHK Luxury Villa with Private Pool", "slug": "premium-4bhk-luxury-villa-kochi", "description": "A stunning 4BHK luxury villa located in a peaceful gated community in Kakkanad, Kochi. This beautifully designed home offers spacious bedrooms, a modern modular kitchen, large living and dining areas, a private swimming pool, landscaped garden, and covered parking. The villa features premium interiors, large windows for natural lighting, and excellent ventilation. Located close to InfoPark, schools, hospitals, and shopping centers, making it perfect for comfortable family living.", "price": "18500000.00", "location": "Kakkanad, Kochi, Kerala", "category": 1, "owner": null, "agent": null, "listing_type": "Sale", "bedrooms": 0, "bathrooms": 0, "area": 0, "latitude": null, "longitude": null, "featured_image": "image/upload/v1772709281/u5jwwkr0l8y142ufwn2h.png", "is_featured": false, "is_available": true, "created_at": "2026-03-04T06:29:08.751Z"}}, {"model": "properties.property", "pk": 5, "fields": {"title": "Prime Residential Plot Near Smart City Kochi", "slug": "prime-residential-plot-smartcity-kochi", "description": "A prime residential plot located near Smart City and InfoPark in Kakkanad, Kochi. This well-connected property is ideal for building a dream home or investment. The plot is situated in a peaceful residential area with good road access, electricity, and water availability. Close to schools, hospitals, supermarkets, and major IT hubs, making it a perfect location for future development.", "price": "4800000.00", "location": "Kakkanad, Kochi, Kerala", "category": 2, "owner": 6, "agent": null, "listing_type": "Sale", "bedrooms": 0, "bathrooms": 0, "area": 0, "latitude": null, "longitude": null, "featured_image": "image/upload/v1772873226/qemczwt5zk8ewst7gwrc.png", "is_featured": true, "is_available": true, "created_at": "2026-03-07T08:47:07.567Z"}}, {"model": "properties.property", "pk": 6, "fields": {"title": "Modern Commercial Office Space in MG Road", "slug": "commercial-p